701
00:37:12.663 --> 00:37:14.258
<i>I mean. you made the hot list.</i>

702
00:37:14.282 --> 00:37:15.848
They said you had the best...

703
00:37:15.917 --> 00:37:17.929
<i>I hear you two
like a guy between you.</i>

704
00:37:17.953 --> 00:37:20.114
<i>Did Justin finger you?
I bet you went down on him.</i>

705
00:37:20.138 --> 00:37:21.298
<i>And they all became you.</i>

706
